0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新一代80</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.photostore.me/images/2016/12/30/ScreenShot2016-12-30at2.55.54PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.photostore.me%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2FScreenShot2016-12-30at2.55.54PM.png&h=d3d6c787&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40be86be180322706bdf28202432fd1d0a57d702","tid":15545,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"呢個48美金咁平。係咪只係行政費用<br />\n<br />\n如果60歲 3萬美金 吸煙 應該幾多錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果已經戒煙幾個月 可唔可以改返冇食煙個rates"},{"pid":"9d30764b320da16d2ad267b886e518fbf84dbc0d","tid":15545,"uid":65425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"睇錯 人妻篇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f30d6fef4a2ba64be4313c227c4797091a13244","tid":15545,"uid":924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"保誠個理想人生係咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d415011f2e1ae2a59b52924d35f2528c639d64ec","tid":15545,"uid":43731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保誠個理想人生係咪伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n儲錢加身固賠償大dddddddd，頭十年還好"},{"pid":"a9933776368c0fbfb3a4b4550e6f91b201668d80","tid":15545,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034e3e2a88e8708e7df2af20658668fac55594f2","tid":15545,"uid":59211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j0HlDd3vOhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj0HlDd3vOhc&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=5a67d16c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j0HlDd3vOhc</a><br />\n<br />\n大家有時間可以睇下, 邱正弘博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n清晒買保險嘅 concept<br />\n<br />\n保險就保險, 投資就投資, 退休就退休<br />\n<br />\n好多人成日諗住買保險要回本, 要計回報, 計irr, 計payback<br />\n所以先會咁多人中左伏, 買左D 保終身嘅保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試諗下, 去到四五十歲, 仔女出晒身, 樓又供完, 如果 touchwood 死左仲有無責任要負?<br />\n<br />\n買保險當香油錢, 洗左買個安心, 你唔會希望拎得返筆錢, 有錢拎表示你已經出左事<br />\n佢有講到, 如果想保險賺錢, 計回報, 好簡單 : 買張2000萬嘅life, 行出大馬路比車撞死<br />\n咁就係最大嘅 return<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生仔, 唔洗養家, 比較需要係'意外險', 出意外唔驚死, 係驚殘廢<br />\n結左婚/要養/仔女細讀緊書/供緊樓, 就真係要買個 term life, term 危疾<br />\n要諗退休, 要諗回報, 就正正經去投資, 去月供基金/股票<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 ..."},{"pid":"319d6fec73bb032bbdda6f0da8e2b6828b392e02","tid":15545,"uid":37066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">financial advisor 先最呃人，扮冇代表單一保險公司，所以中立。<br />\n收皮啦！咪又係sell最高commission rate 果間公司既保險。<br />\n知道哂你果行既黑幕啦，咪撚扮中立啦！</span>"},{"pid":"9f1a77d473a8cd26c9bcbf9508b564cb8078feb1","tid":15545,"uid":102227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"長知識了"},{"pid":"0a2ece48ea033bbdd38083fc4cd279de86193771","tid":15545,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"幫小朋友買定人壽<br />\n供10年包到80歲果啲好唔好<br />\n我見香港人壽有"},{"pid":"c43425525551eb71b9442d243a96fbec9d196bb2","tid":15545,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫小朋友買定人壽<br />\n供10年包到80歲果啲好唔好<br />\n我見香港人壽有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慳番d 錢幫佢買醫療好過"}]}